            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="floating-badge">
          <span class="floating-badge-icon">🔒</span>
          <div>
            <div class="floating-badge-text">HIPAA Compliant</div>
            <div class="floating-badge-sub">End-to-end encrypted</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
       STATS BAR
  ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-big">50K+</div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Registered patients</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-big">1,200</div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Verified doctors</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-big">320</div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Partner pharmacies</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-big">99.8%</div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Platform uptime</div>
    </div>
  </div>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
       HOW IT WORKS
  ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section" id="how-it-works">
    <p class="section-label">How it works</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">From registration to care in three steps</h2>
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-icon">👤</div>
        <h3>Create your profile</h3>
        <p>Register as a patient, doctor, or pharmacist. Your role determines your dashboard and everything you can access on the platform.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-icon">🔗</div>
        <h3>Connect with your care team</h3>
        <p>Patients find and book appointments with verified doctors. Doctors review patient records. Pharmacists manage prescriptions — all coordinated in one place.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-icon">📋</div>
        <h3>Manage your care</h3>
        <p>Track appointments, view lab results, send prescriptions, and communicate securely. Every interaction is logged and encrypted.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
       WHO IT'S FOR
  ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="roles-section" id="roles">
    <p class="section-label" style="color:var(--teal);">Built for everyone in the care cycle</p>
    <h2 class="section-title" style="color:#fff;">Three roles. One connected platform.</h2>
    <div class="roles-grid">

      <div class="role-card patient">
        <h3>Patients</h3>
        <p>Book appointments, view test results, request prescription refills, and keep your entire health history in one secure place.</p>
        <a href="/register" class="role-card-link">Register as a patient →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="role-card doctor">
        <h3>Doctors</h3>
        <p>Manage your schedule, access patient records, write prescriptions, and consult with specialists — all from your dashboard.</p>
        <a href="/register" class="role-card-link">Join as a doctor →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="role-card pharmacy">
        <h3>Pharmacists</h3>
        <p>Receive digital prescriptions, verify patient eligibility, and coordinate medication dispensing with minimal paperwork.</p>
        <a href="/register" class="role-card-link">Register your pharmacy →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
       FEATURES
  ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="features-section" id="features">
    <div class="features-inner">
      <div>
        <p class="section-label">Platform features</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Everything your care team needs</h2>
        <div class="features-list">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div>
              <h4>Smart appointment scheduling</h4>
              <p>Patients book in seconds. Doctors confirm instantly. No more phone tag or double-bookings.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div>
              <h4>Unified patient records</h4>
              <p>Every visit, test result, and prescription in one timeline — accessible to the right people, at the right time.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div>
              <h4>Secure in-app messaging</h4>
              <p>HIPAA-compliant messaging between patients, doctors, and pharmacists. No emails, no insecure channels.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <div>
              <h4>Real-time notifications</h4>
              <p>Appointment reminders, prescription updates, and lab result alerts — so nothing falls through the cracks.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Chat visual -->
