        <div class="chat-label">Dr. Obi · 9:42 AM</div>
        <div class="chat-bubble">Your latest blood panel looks good. I've updated your chart and sent a note to your pharmacist about your refill.</div>
        <div class="chat-label right">You · 9:45 AM</div>
        <div class="chat-bubble right">Thank you! Will I need to come in next week?</div>
        <div class="chat-label">Dr. Obi · 9:47 AM</div>
        <div class="chat-bubble">No need — I'll schedule a follow-up in 30 days. I've added it to your calendar automatically. 🗓️</div>
        <div class="chat-prescription">

          <div>
            <div class="chat-presc-title">Prescription sent to pharmacy</div>
            <div class="chat-presc-sub">HealthFirst Pharmacy · Est. ready 2:00 PM</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════
       TESTIMONIALS
  ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
